data.description: Come see the home of your dreams! This charming property boasts an inviting enclosed front porch for those cozy mornings for sipping coffee or enjoying an evening breeze. That is just the beginning here! Safety and peace of mind come standard at this property with a personal underground storm shelter in the front room. Culinary enthusiasts will adore this spacious, open kitchen with plenty of counter top space and cabinets. Don't forget the built in pantry! An elegant brick mantel and fire place in the living room gives you that wonderful cozy at home feeling. Storage worries are a thing of the past thanks to the abundance of space throughout this home! If you are not sold already come see this expansive, sun dappled back yard. With ample yard space and a covered back porch this yard is the perfect addition to an already amazing property. There is a built-in gardening run for all the plant lovers that could also be converted to have more yard space. The possibilities for this property are endless. No matter family size or house hold needs, this property has something for everyone! Schedule a tour now this one won't last! Conveniently located moments from major highway access for any commute. Seconds from the Paseo District and in the heart of the Asian District the adventures, food and shopping are waiting for you!
